  <title>Change the wallpaper</title>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Click the system menu on the bottom left corner of your screen and press
       the <gui>Settings</gui> button in the middle of the menu.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>From the list of items, select <gui>Background</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click the current background image in the center of the
       <gui>Background</gui> window.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click the background image you want to use.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click the <gui>Select</gui> button.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Close the <gui>Background</gui> window by clicking the cross at the
     top-right corner of the window.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

